Who We Are For Clients
In The News















 











Paradigm Financial Advisors






























 
Who we are... 
Paradigm Financial Advisors is a private wealth management and advisory firm which offers investors both traditional diversified portfolio models as well as our exclusive �Wealth Builder� investment program.  Regardless of the program, our focus is to:

Protect our clients’ assets from severe market downturns. 
Grow our clients’ wealth with above average market returns. 
Generate a stable, lifetime monthly income for our clients during their retirement.

The Ideal Portfolio? 
Although we recognize that a perfect portfolio is unrealistic, our signature “Wealth Builder” portfolio incorporates the features most important to us, our clients and, we believe, to many other responsible investors. These features include: 

 Traditionally Conservative Risk level as measured by Standard Deviation and Traditional Stock to Bond Ratios 
 Limited, BUT still, 100% Equivalent Exposure to the Stock market - for higher potential returns 
 Takes advantage of Dollar Cost Averaging 
 Can provide reasonably consistent monthly income 
 Is simple to understand and manage 
 Doesn’t require a lot of time and attention/effort 
 Doesn’t depend on market timing (ability to predict the future) 
 Back testing results have consistently outperformed the S&P 500tm Index over mid to long terms 
 Low expenses and fees 
 Doesn’t require a lot of trading in and out of positions 
 Gives you complete control of your investments 
 Doesn’t have any penalties associated with accessing your money 
 Is less volatile than the market as a whole, therefore it can be less stressful 

What you must believe. 
In order to work successfully with us, our clients must share the fundamental beliefs upon which our investment method is based. These are:

We do not believe in fortune tellers, i.e. we do not believe that anyone can predict the future. Therefore, we will not put our life’s earnings and future prosperity in their hands to gamble with. 
We believe that the US stock market will perform in the same manner that it has for the last 114 years. In other words it will fluctuate up and down. 
We believe that in the long run, Capitalism (and thus the US economy) will continue to grow due to:
        
An ever increasing population (demand). 



Technological innovations. 
The innate human desire to progress and improve its’ condition. 

We understand that it is more important to avoid losses in our portfolio than it is to try and overcome them with exceptional gains. 

If you accept and agree with the above, then we believe you will be interested in what we have to offer. 
 Who our clients are.  We work with people that: 

Have money worth protecting. 
Want to achieve higher than average returns with less risk. 
Want to develop a consistent, dependable income during retirement. 
Want to understand what they own in their portfolio and why. 
Are more concerned with results than image. 
Are realistic and pragmatic. 
Can recognize opportunity.
Are tired of risking their assets in the Wall Street Casino. 


 




b


















 Bill and Leah  have over 30 years of combined experience in the financial services industry. "Managing our clients' wealth and retirement savings is a huge privilege and responsibility. We strive to provide the most competent and enlightened  advice and personal service."


 











 



