Why Choose Paradigm Financial Advisors?


Paradigm Financial Advisors, LLC, is an SEC Registered Investment Advisor.
We provide comprehensive Wealth Management services for our clients. We utilize a team approach in analyzing and planning a client’s investment portfolio, estate plan, cash flow, income tax planning, and retirement goals. All recommendations are based solely on your specific needs, circumstances and goals. We serve our clients in a fiduciary capacity and pledge to act in our clients’ best interest at all times.  Assets are managed in a prudent, disciplined fashion with emphasis placed on risk management, low cost and consistent results.









